{"tid":1788580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36歲陳蕊蕊狠撇爛滾金剛 大隻仔新歡曝光","createTime":"2019-12-18T19:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T12:10:07.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"55ad9280ac15efa66155d8b5b58c3a27f33f7f2e","tid":1788580,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:19:23.000Z","msg":"陳蕊蕊同金剛拍拖最終難頂男方愛蒲爛滾忍痛分手，金剛同34D台灣女友Nana拍拖以來 不時放閃，而陳蕊蕊單身三年都未聽聞感情有著落，次次見親記者都呻冇人敢追喎，聽落 好陰功豬囉！原來唔聲唔聲，新歡已登場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1_939a_aunt_p20_16302241705dfa1a32378e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1_939a_aunt_p20_16302241705dfa1a32378e2.jpg&h=f5483f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年藝人金剛同擁有34F導彈身材的女友陳蕊蕊拍拖近三年，經常都高調曬愛，可惜最終都未能開花結果。"},{"pid":"68ae2ba2d1bf1751140e5c4a91ced004f696634f","tid":1788580,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/f_1148a_aunt_p12_13_14328483685dfa19747d2a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Ff_1148a_aunt_p12_13_14328483685dfa19747d2a0.jpg&h=6cddcbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n演藝事業以外，陳蕊蕊呢兩年積極搵朋友拍檔學做生意，繼明星學院後，早前又開格仔舖親自出席開幕儀式。"},{"pid":"4bb3fade1889e6a7bc19bb6d943c4422ebd2dfee","tid":1788580,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:19:53.000Z","msg":"神秘新歡曝光鍾情大隻仔<br />\n<br />\n日前蕊蕊出席完活 動，滾水淥腳收拾離場，場外就有大隻猛男接收工，等到蕊蕊之後一齊行去攞車，再同車 返埋去清水灣半島香閨，似乎已經發展到同居階段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/e_1148a_aunt_p12_13_16361871645dfa19731f364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Fe_1148a_aunt_p12_13_16361871645dfa19731f364.jpg&h=7722ea6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1703719733d6a58d46f3424f32d7f54415353f","tid":1788580,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"其實睇勻歷任男友，蕊蕊對大隻仔情有獨鍾，除咗金剛仲有曾經同周秀娜拍過拖嘅陳偉成，個個大隻仔最終都係衰愛蒲爛滾搞到分手收場，今次又埋大隻仔身，希望帶眼識人 打破宿命啦！"},{"pid":"99d883b54c72db1e4200025846c1247d630afac9","tid":1788580,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:27:40.000Z","msg":"好撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d8f4943b0e7b7c1f61b8dd10dbd28520a4f60e","tid":1788580,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T19:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6rhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=01dcbb6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6rhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=346393a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c0d5fd1deb319c9af66c64d2e2e2c6bdf7efd9f","tid":1788580,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"好撚老"},{"pid":"860cfbb408f98436ab02c6f9c0773356ec2a8d79","tid":1788580,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"佢又住到清水灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/h